ng energies as a function of the mixing parameter of hybrid DFT,\nwe conjecture that a necessary condition for a pure excitonic insulator is that\nits noninteracting electronic structure is metallic.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 May 2018 16:12:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-12"}
